        <item>
            <title>Version 2.2.4</title>
            <sparkle:version>2.2.4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.0.17763</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 14:23:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Remio Host 2.2.4</h2>
                <p>This update makes streaming far more resilient on machines where the graphics driver misbehaves. Remio Host now re-checks your GPU's hardware encoder after every reboot instead of staying on slower software encoding for days, and it automatically restarts itself if video encoding ever gets stuck - so a black screen or 'video isn't working' state recovers on its own instead of waiting for a manual restart.</p>
            ]]></description>
